00:12:24.600 --> 00:12:25.600
ke Rumah Mutiara Selatan.

00:12:25.600 --> 00:12:27.840
Saya tidak mendapat satu syiling pun daripadanya.

00:12:41.600 --> 00:12:43.200
Anda tidak mempunyai wang.

00:12:44.480 --> 00:12:46.440
Kemudian ia seolah-olah mengekalkan anda di sini

00:12:46.440 --> 00:12:48.040
adalah sia-sia.

00:12:49.720 --> 00:12:50.640
Apa yang anda maksudkan, tidak berguna?

00:12:50.640 --> 00:12:51.240
Ah!

00:12:51.520 --> 00:12:52.800
Hei, jelaskan diri anda, idola!

00:12:52.880 --> 00:12:53.560
saya...

00:12:54.800 --> 00:12:55.720
awak buat apa?

00:12:56.080 --> 00:12:57.240
lepaskan saya!

00:12:57.240 --> 00:12:57.760
saya...

00:12:58.520 --> 00:12:59.240
Pergi.

00:13:02.480 --> 00:13:04.400
Tak pasal-pasal aku rasa pening.

00:13:06.360 --> 00:13:07.360
Ikat dia.

00:13:08.040 --> 00:13:08.560
ya.

00:13:08.880 --> 00:13:09.520
Hei!

00:13:09.520 --> 00:13:10.240
Tidak, tidak, tidak!

00:13:11.920 --> 00:13:12.480
buang dia.

00:13:13.560 --> 00:13:14.080
saya...

00:13:14.360 --> 00:13:14.920
Berhenti!

00:13:15.640 --> 00:13:16.120
Ah!

